    <h1>Largest Contentful Paint (LCP)</h1>
    <p class="description">A Core Web Vitals metric measuring how fast the largest visible element on a page renders. Good LCP is <strong>under 2.5 seconds</strong> — slow LCP is a direct Google ranking disadvantage.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
